detaileddescription.para: Benchmark to compare performance of reading Parquet decimal data using vectorized Iceberg read path and the built-in file source in Spark.

To run this benchmark for spark-3.3: ./gradlew -DsparkVersions=3.3 :iceberg-spark:iceberg-spark-3.3_2.12:jmh \ -PjmhIncludeRegex=VectorizedReadParquetDecimalBenchmark \ -PjmhOutputPath=benchmark/results.txt
Benchmark to compare performance of reading Parquet decimal data using vectorized Iceberg read path and the built-in file source in Spark.

To run this benchmark for spark-3.5: ./gradlew -DsparkVersions=3.5 :iceberg-spark:iceberg-spark-3.5_2.12:jmh \ -PjmhIncludeRegex=VectorizedReadParquetDecimalBenchmark \ -PjmhOutputPath=benchmark/results.txt
